{"tid":1468471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地冇分勇武定和理，出得黎都係手足！","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:12:44.000Z","uid":5967,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"357b20eb1d7753704651206daef04e6f3b0921f8","tid":1468471,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:48:48.000Z","msg":"立即停止分化<br />\n記唔記得2014年點輸？<br />\n<br />\n衝就係鬼<br />\n守就係鬼<br />\n拆大台就鬼<br />\n起大台就鬼<br />\n<br />\n而家機場要避免重新變成金鐘comfort zone 既盲點<br />\n<br />\n同時要打破思想盲點<br />\n停止再用勇武同和理分類手足<br />\n<br />\n衝立會既手足，可以今晚選擇去靜坐唔圍狗<br />\n同樣坐左4日既手足，可能突然火遮眼，出去打狗，圍狗<br />\n<br />\n咁以上既手足，你應該稱呼佢係勇武定係和理？<br />\n<br />\n突破思想盲點，停止限制自己角色<br />\n<br />\n你今日係和理，聽日可以係勇武<br />\n<br />\n停止切割，停止分化<br />\n<br />\n保護手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">學生係手足，銀髮係手足，西裝友係，媽媽係，師奶，良心紀律部隊係。醫護係，記者係，打工仔係，地盤師兄係！<br />\n<br />\n你，你，你同你，都係手足。 <br />\n<br />\n我地未必100%做得好，但會檢討。<br />\n<br />\n出得黎，就係憑良知，憑信念。<br />\n<br />\n點都好，手足做咩都好，齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n真香港人，核爆都唔割<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n黑警，以眼還眼</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c8c389358a11876d4c040c734abe2b20bb2d570e","tid":1468471,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/241gDjd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F241gDjd.jpg&h=24184809&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3FpNcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3FpNcz.jpg&h=7d30142c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDEudSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDEudSz.jpg&h=51c08fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RW360xA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRW360xA.jpg&h=82f5ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKyuYjf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKyuYjf.jpg&h=abda31c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SqmDREf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSqmDREf.jpg&h=86ba4115&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jUudSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7jUudSB.jpg&h=7ccf2950&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0918140ca4b3fe9b6e9bbcbba89d52c793d7ac56","tid":1468471,"uid":5967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:51:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位手足<br />\nAssemble <br />\n<br />\n6個死士，一隻眼球，七百個手足<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"496b117a2f193f9c6402d6b19536a43a6bb0f796","tid":1468471,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:57:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bd2cd8b7eb6ef181422d4ae3dfcd10c61288d2b","tid":1468471,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:41:27.000Z","msg":"冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a4dbeda3d2f47b7b8fabfab146b484453f0a7d","tid":1468471,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:53:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e362fafe25b8b238641bf7f8292534fa3741be17","tid":1468471,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"65f39e94a3ea1c9a1d4ed924ef15056aa707ca22","tid":1468471,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:44:20.000Z","msg":"又沉底"},{"pid":"a9e7042e3660989a20e9b0390738430365b09dde","tid":1468471,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"4abbd4f5fb116c3dffa16216a871ef06c68857de","tid":1468471,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:05:58.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇到"},{"pid":"3d66b498fb713721a28e36d3454bdf